### Ingest a transaction
POST http://localhost:5080/webhooks/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "tx-2026-0001",
  "amount": 250.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "timestamp": "2026-05-01T10:15:00Z",
  "status": "Completed"
}

### Replay the same transaction (idempotency check — same response, no duplicate row)
POST http://localhost:5080/webhooks/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "tx-2026-0001",
  "amount": 250.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "timestamp": "2026-05-01T10:15:00Z",
  "status": "Completed"
}

### Invalid payload (returns 400 with validation problem details)
POST http://localhost:5080/webhooks/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "",
  "amount": -5,
  "currency": "us",
  "timestamp": "0001-01-01T00:00:00Z",
  "status": "what"
}
